elp me find it...Please!!!!!<br>
<br>
Dh wants to move us to Kentucky, expecting me to teach there.  I went online to see it there were any jobs, and found none.  Come to find out through his family there, they don't advertise or fly their openings, they hire by word of mouth through people they know.<br>
<br>
Now, that's not some place I want to work and it's not the way I'd want to be hired.  Dh isn't getting it, so I need the law as proof.<br>
<br>
I told him if I (or he) sent my resume down, it would have to be accompanied by a law suit for unfair hiring practices. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :hat --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/pimp.gif ALT=":hat"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
