<br>
In AZ there are hardly advertisements for teaching either if memory serves and things haven't changed too much in the last 8 years or so, but you put your resume/application in at each district and get the screening interview then see about a follow up. <br>
<br>
&quot;Come to find out through his family there, they don't advertise or fly their openings, they hire by word of mouth through people they know.&quot;<br>
<br>
Companies can be as formal as they want to, and yes many may get hired through job fairs and blind resumes, but I hardly know anyone hired this way anywhere. Sad truth is most of us are referred or have a friend or relative at whatever place we are now working. Not to say it gets you the job, but it definitely gets you the interview. <br>
<br>
&quot;I told him if I (or he) sent my resume down, it would have to be accompanied by a law suit for unfair hiring practices.&quot;<br>
<br>
I'm not sure what you mean here, but I'm hoping the copy of the law suit is for dh and not a prospective employer. You would find yourself weeded out very swiftly officially or no if ya did that<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Only thing I can recommend is sweeping all the districts in which you wish to work and make as many contacts as you can through family and when you move there. Plus you don't know how much stock to put in dh's family's assessment, maybe there are folks getting hired off the street and they just don't know it. Either way, I don't think the law will help much since you can't use it unless you can prove you were slighted or denied and that is EXTREMELY difficult, especially if you don't yet have an interview. People in my company get jobs all the time that are never even posted or were posted as a gesture only--they already knew who they were going to take (dh benefitted from this just recently himself).<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
ST <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#9fb7df><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Mony</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#3333ff>(4/23/03 9:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/freligiousdebate60574frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=195.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Hiring in KY</span><hr size=1> Kelly, <br>
