<br>
On a side note, I found it interesting that the Board of Ed in KY was immune from suit for permitting a sexual harassment offendor to operate for 16 years unpunished in their school district despite numerous complaints.  When sued they claimed Sovreign Immunity and dismissed all the charges.<br>
<br>
You sure you want to live there? <p>DBC67<br>
